The annual lawnmowers world championships took place in Heddington, Wiltshire, England from July 2 to 3, with 16 races in each of the categories. Graham Tibbenham (No. 123) was declared the world champion in Group 2, Sean Transwell (No. 18) in group 3 and Kenny Goodesmith (No. 66 - Orange trousers) in group 4. (With input from AP)